name: Commsecure
overview: CommSecure Limited provides e-commerce solutions to large billers, financial institutions, and other online payment companies in Australia and Hong Kong. The company offers electronic billing and payments solutions, including e-billing, e-payments, IVR phone payments, direct debit payments and management, customer self-serve and call centre applications, reconciliation, archiving, and real time stock market information. Its e-business solutions and services comprise BillSecure, an integrated e-billing and payment management solution; PaySecure, a secure payments gateway to facilitate electronic payments for credit card and direct debit; DDRSecure, an electronic direct debit management and payment solution; IVRSecure, an integrated phone and payment management solution; and MarketSecure, which provides online real-time equities trading information.
